evergreen /ˈɛvəˌɡriːn/

(evergreens) 

1. N-COUNT An evergreen is a tree or bush that has green leaves all year long. 常青树; 常绿植物 

例： Holly, like ivy and mistletoe, is an evergreen. 冬青与常春藤和槲寄生一样，也是一种常绿植物。 

2. ADJ Evergreen is also an adjective. 常绿的 

例： Plant evergreen shrubs around the end of the month. 大约在月末种植常绿灌木。

